public enemy ( hangul : 공공의 적 ; rr : gonggongui jeok ) is a 2002 south korean film directed by kang woo-suk .   the film was well received by audiences and critics alike , being seen by almost 3 million people in south korea , while winning sol kyung-gu best actor at the grand bell awards and blue dragon film awards for his lead role .   the success of the film led to the making of the sequel another public enemy in 2005 .